KitKat::

She finally stretched and awoke fully in the CR chamber.  She watched 
as the links and connections disengaged and the chamer opened up for 
her.  She stepped out and looked around. Her nose told her she wasn't 
in a pred base.  She transformed into wolf mode and started BASE 
INTRUDER ALERT STARTED SOUNDING OFF.  She closed her optics and 
winces, "Damn, this just isn't my eon is it?" she muttered and 
prepared for battle.
